feedback_meta.text:
-= Kitchen =-
Well how about that, you are in the place we're calling the kitchen.

You see a fridge. What a letdown! The fridge is empty! You see an oven. You can see a table. You see a cookbook on the table. You idly wonder how they came up with the name TextWorld for this place. It's pretty fitting. You can see a counter. You see a knife on the counter. You hear a noise behind you and spin around, but you can't see anything other than a stove. You wonder idly who left that here. Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it.

There is a closed frosted-glass door leading east. There is an open patio door leading west. You don't like doors? Why not try going north, that entranceway is not blocked by one. There is an exit to the south. Don't worry, there is no door.
